narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend Italian II to another student because you learn a whole lot and Italian is a wonderful language to learn.
You do 4 more chapters of the book, then cultural stuff and review. By the end, I felt fairly competent in my italian abilities.
The class is pretty interesting, fun, and useful. The language is beautiful.
I would. If you enjoyed L1, this is really just a continuation of that.
